<div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-20">
  <div class="text-center max-w-md">
    <div class="text-9xl font-bold text-primary/10 mb-4">404</div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
      <% if(lang==='uz'){%>Sahifa topilmadi<%}else if(lang==='ru'){%>Страница не найдена<%}else{%>Page Not Found<%}%>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">
      <% if(lang==='uz'){%>Siz qidirgan sahifa mavjud emas yoki ko'chirilgan.<%}else if(lang==='ru'){%>Страница, которую вы ищете, не существует или была перемещена.<%}else{%>The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved.<%}%>
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-xl font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition flex items-center gap-2">
        <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
        <% if(lang==='uz'){%>Bosh sahifa<%}else if(lang==='ru'){%>Главная<%}else{%>Go Home<%}%>
      </a>
      <button onclick="history.back()" class="px-6 py-3 border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 transition flex items-center gap-2">
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
        <% if(lang==='uz'){%>Orqaga<%}else if(lang==='ru'){%>Назад<%}else{%>Go Back<%}%>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
